                        OMAHA, NEB.</p>
                </figure>
                
                <note><hi rend="underline">over</hi></note>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    OMAHA
                    APR 5
                    1 230 PM
                    1920
                    NEBR.
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>John Neihardt</addrLine>
