                    Permanent address: 
                    Ingleside
                    <hi rend="caps">R.F.D.</hi> 4
                
                    Norristown
                    Penn.
                </ab>
                
                <note place="bottom" type="recipient">From Dhou Muherji
                    after his visit
                    at my home, J.G.N.</note>
                
                <figure/>
                
